      <hedline>
        <hl1>'You Don't Have To Take the Bait'</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Rick Melamed letter on Robert Mackey's May 21 Lives column calls undercover investigators bottom feederss</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>It appears that personal-injury lawyers are no longer the bottom feeders of the occupational food chain. India as a ''catch your husband cheating'' professional takes the prize. She has found an occupation that makes the lawyers look good.</p>
        <p>Rick Melamed</p>
        <p>New York</p>
